import scala.util.parsing.json.JSON
import org.apache.spark.SparkContext
import org.apache.spark.SparkConf
import scala.math._
import org.apache.spark.rdd._

  case class Allo (
                     title:     String,
                     ownRating : String,
                     director : String,
                     spectators_reviews:        String,
                     date : String,
                     id : String
                   ) extends java.io.Serializable

  def parser(movie: String): Map[String, Any] =
    JSON.parseFull(movie).get.asInstanceOf[Map[String, Any]]

  def exploreMovie(movieList : String) : Allo =  {
    val json = parser(movieList)
    Allo(json("title").toString,
      json("ownRating").toString,
      json("director").toString,
      json("spectators_reviews").toString,
      json("date").toString,
      json("id").toString
      )
  }
